  "title": "Repair Sales Engineer (MANUFACTURING MNC/East) - Entry Level/up to $4200 #HAO",
  "description": "<p>Salary: up to $4200</p><p>Working Days & Hours: Mon-Fri Office Hours</p><p>Location: Kaki Bukit</p><p>Job Description:</p><ul><li><strong>Sales Generation:</strong> Actively seek repair leads, perform site surveys, and present proposals to customers to meet sales and profitability goals.</li><li><strong>Technical Support:</strong> Collaborate with field technicians and operations to identify repair needs, troubleshoot, and prepare accurate technical estimates.</li><li><strong>Customer Relationship Management:</strong> Build rapport with clients, handle inquiries, and provide technical solutions for elevator performance issues.</li><li><strong>Quote & Contract Negotiation:</strong> Prepare detailed quotations, negotiate terms, and ensure compliance with safety codes and company standards.</li><li><strong>Safety Compliance:</strong> Ensure all repair work complies with regulatory, safety, and quality standards. </li></ul><p>Job Requirements: Min Degree in Engineering or similar </p><p>Interested candidates, please submit your resume to: allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>Ally Audrey Lok Xin Woon</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifescience)</p><p>Company EA Licence number : 99C4599</p><p>Personnel EA License: R21102307</p><p><a href=\"mailto:allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg</a></p>",
